Author: boo_snug
Text: Lol that’s what grandma’s do. We would see my grandparents occasionally, once a month, or every few months for big holidays, birthdays, etc, and that’s what they *do* - stock up on our favorite foods, snacks, big dinners, etc. As I’ve gotten older I’ve gotten better at not eating everything in sight, but when I was kid I would go ham on all the sweets. Lmao love my grandma.
